            "en_US": "<p>Penn State Clinical and Translational Science Institute accelerates discoveries to benefit human health.</p>\n<p>It is a bridge between basic scientists and clinical researchers and promotes collaboration to discover new treatments, medical procedures and ways to diagnose disease. It helps the Penn State community move its health research more efficiently and effectively out of the science laboratories and into use by the people who need it.</p>"
